    ðŸ”¹ `col -l <number>` --> ðŸ”¢ Limit `col`'s buffer to `number` lines.
    ðŸ”¹ `col -h` --> â“ Display help information.
    ðŸ”¹ `col -V` --> â„¹ï¸ Display the command's version.

